---
import Layout from "../../../components/layout/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Licences"
  description="Licences du code et du contenu d'Open Ordinal."
  lang="fr"
  canonical="https://openordinal.org/fr/legal/licenses"
>
  <section class="archive-shell entry-prose">
    <h1 class="text-[46px] leading-tight text-ink">Licences</h1>

    <p class="ui-meta text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-dim">Derniere mise a jour: 2026-03-03</p>

    <h2>Resume des licences</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Code: MIT</li>
      <li>Contenu et donnees: CC BY 4.0</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Format d'attribution</h2>
    <p>Utiliser: <code>Open Ordinal / openordinal.org (CC BY 4.0)</code>.</p>

    <h2>Composants tiers</h2>
    <p>Les logiciels et services tiers utilises par ce projet restent soumis a leurs propres licences et conditions.</p>

    <h2>Fichiers de licence</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/openordinal/open-ordinal/blob/main/LICENSE-code.txt" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Fichier licence MIT</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/openordinal/open-ordinal/blob/main/LICENSE-content.txt" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Fichier licence CC BY 4.0</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Texte legal CC BY 4.0</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
